Package: shinyProxyTest
Type: Package
Title: Implements a demo shiny application inside a package
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Mark Sellors
Maintainer: Mark Sellos <msellors@mango-solutions.com>
Description: A small package that implements the 'geyser' shiny app inside a 
    package.
    The geyser shiny app is the small app provided by the RStudio IDE when you
    click to create a new "Shiny Web App...".
    In this package that shiny app has been broken up into parts as a
    demonstration of how one might approach the packaging of such an app.
    The main idea is from here. 
    https://www.mango-solutions.com/packaging-shiny-applications-a-deep-dive/
    https://rtask.thinkr.fr/our-shiny-template-to-design-a-prod-ready-app/
    https://rtask.thinkr.fr/building-a-shiny-app-as-a-package/
    https://rtask.thinkr.fr/building-big-shiny-apps-a-workflow-1/
    https://rtask.thinkr.fr/building-big-shiny-apps-a-workflow-2/
    https://r-pkgs.org/
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
